The paper deals with optimization algorithms for a RAKE receiver in an ultra-wideband system, which involves signal processing, communication theory, and optimization. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also involves networked systems (cs.NI), control systems (cs.SY), machine learning (cs.MM), and optimization (cs.LG).
